entries.title_d: Escort the Royal Freighters Through Ay'Nat held space
entries.title: Naboo System: Duty: Escort Freighters
entries.thanks_5: Any chance you looking for a new career as bodyguard?
entries.thanks_4: Hahaha, they will think twice before attacking us again!
entries.thanks_3: Splendid, finally a RSF pilot that knows what they're doing!
entries.thanks_2: Back in my day, I would have dealt with those pirates twice as fast..
entries.thanks_1: Great job pilot, lets hurry out of here!
entries.taunt_5: I'll guide you back down to Naboo RSF weakling, without your ship of course.
entries.taunt_4: You're attacking us in that hunk of junk RSF? You can't be serious.
entries.taunt_3: I will enjoy cutting your ship in half RSF puppet!
entries.taunt_2: We're boarding this ship, now it's just a question if you want to die for it or not.
entries.taunt_1: The RSF are a bunch of cowards!
entries.shields_depleted: Our shields are down! If you don't get rid of those pilotes, we are done for!
entries.reason_5: Greetings pilot, good to see you. Lets head for the surface quickly, I don't want any incidents.
entries.reason_4: Perfect, a RSF pilot. Last time we didn't get an escort and those Ay'Nat Legion pirates put my ship in the docks for a month!
entries.reason_3: My job depends on me making this transport on time, so I hope you know what you are doing pilot.
entries.reason_2: Thank you for escorting us pilot. We've had trouble out here before so, stay alert!
entries.reason_1: There you are. I hope you're good at this, the Queen's cargo attracts every pirate in the sector...
entries.quest_rendezvous_d: Meet the Freighter here for Escort
entries.quest_location_d: Trade route in the Naboo System
entries.quest_escort_d: A freighter belonging to the royal seat of Naboo
entries.panic_5: Oh no! Pirates! After the Queen's personal cargo!
entries.panic_4: Oh no, Ay'Nat Legion! You better be good at your job pilot!
entries.panic_2: Pirate wretches, they want the Queen's cargo!
entries.hull_half: Our sensors register multiple hull breeches, you have to take care of those pirates now!
entries.goodbye_5: I'd like to come back in a different ships and teach those scum a thing or two. Anyway, thank you for the help pilot!
entries.goodbye_4: That was a close one and your the only reason we survived. Accept our gratitude pilot.
entries.goodbye_3: After this, I'm putting some defense weapons on my freighter. Thanks again my friend.
entries.goodbye_2: Bumpy ride but we made it in one piece thanks to you pilot.
entries.goodbye_1: The Royal Security Force never lets me down, thank you pilot!
entries.found_loc: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Another of Queen Kylantha's freighters has requested an escort. You are commanded to assist. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.failed_protect: The Queen's freighter has been lost...
entries.failed_destroy: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 I can't believe we lost another royal freighter! No doubt the Queen will be furious! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.complete: The Queen will be most pleased! Great job pilot!
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Pirate interceptors have been eliminated. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: <  \#pcontrast1 Pirate Starships on intercept course! General Alert! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_loc: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 One of Queen Kylantha's cargo freighters is on its way. Wait here... \#pcontrast3 >
entries.abort: Aborting as ordered. Preparing escape to hyperspace.
